<H3> <TI>   Travel Warning Issued </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB2301080994 Johannesburg SAPA in English 0743 GMT 23 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> MB2301080994 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg SAPA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pretoria Jan 23 SAPA -- Minister of Foreign Affairs 
Pik Botha on Sunday requested South Africans not to travel to 
Maseru or its surrounding areas because of the fighting that 
broke out there in the morning. "South Africans are requested 
not to travel to maseru and its environs until the situation has 
returned to normal," he said in Pretoria. 

</TEXT>

