<F P=102>  EA2401170094 Nairobi Kenya Broadcasting Corporation Network 
in English 1000 GMT 24 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA2401170094 </F>
<F P=104>  Nairobi Kenya Broadcasting Corporation Network 
