<H3> <TI>   Venda Official Appointed National Force Commander </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  MB2501170894 Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network in 
English 1400 GMT 25 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> MB2501170894 </F>
<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The military ruler of Venda, Brigadier Gabriel 
Ramushwana, has been appointed by the Transitional Executive 
Council [TEC] as commander of the national peace-keeping force. 
With his appointment he renounces the Venda leadership and 
ceases to be a candidate on the ANC [African National Congress] 
election list. Members of the peace force will be deployed 
within the next five weeks following the completion of their 
training near Bloemfontein. 

</TEXT>

