Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulundi Jan 26 SAPA -- The Inkatha Freedom Party's 
[IFP] Central Committee says it is not able prepare 
recommendations on the party's participation in the general 
election for the upcoming IFP national conference because 
constitutional negotiations have not been completed. 
  Trilateral negotiations between the government, the African 
