a member, are to resume on Thursday in a last-ditch effort to 
ensure the alliance's participation in the election. 
  The IFP Central Committee in a statement on Wednesday night 
also expressed concern that the lack of progress in separate 
negotiations on the position of the Zulu king and kingdom would 
