Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Peace talks in Lusaka [words indistinct] specific 
points of the national police dossier [words indistinct] 
modalities for the application of general and specific 
principles. The government delegation is worried because its 
proposal has so far been in agreement with the thinking of the 
mediator and the troika of observers. 
  The numbers proposed by the government for the participation 
