  [Text] Comrades: 
  As 1994 is drawing near, all comrades at XINHUA NEWS AGENCY 
would like to extend their season's greetings to you. They 
would also like to express their thanks for your enthusiastic 
support for the work carried out by the news agency over the 
past year. 
